<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,1441,1610]" pageId="2" pageNumber="523">
<taxonomicName box="[199,432,1513,1538]" class="Insecta" family="Conopidae" genus="Conops" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="523" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longiventris">
<emphasis box="[199,432,1513,1538]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="523">Conops longiventris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is described as a small blackish 
<taxonomicName box="[843,928,1514,1537]" class="Insecta" family="Conopidae" genus="Conops" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="523" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[843,928,1514,1537]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="523">Conops</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with a completely black body. Numerous specimens of 
<taxonomicName box="[307,446,1549,1574]" class="Insecta" family="Conopidae" genus="Conops" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="523" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavifrons">
<emphasis box="[307,446,1549,1574]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="523">C. flavifrons</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
have these characters and there are many intermediates. Although the 
<typeStatus box="[1249,1347,1549,1574]" pageId="2" pageNumber="523">holotype</typeStatus>
has not been investigated, 
<taxonomicName box="[360,527,1585,1610]" class="Insecta" family="Conopidae" genus="Conops" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="523" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longiventris">
<emphasis box="[360,527,1585,1610]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="523">C. longiventris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is herewith placed as a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName box="[1008,1146,1585,1610]" class="Insecta" family="Conopidae" genus="Conops" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="523" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavifrons">
<emphasis box="[1008,1146,1585,1610]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="523">C. flavifrons</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
